---
title: Herby Roasted Chicken with Honey-Mustard Brussels Sprouts and Garlicky Smashed Potatoes
description: We've got you covered for your next special night in with this dish! A brush of thyme and rosemary oil creates fragrant, juicy roasted chicken served alongside creamy garlic-butter smashed potatoes and roasted sprouts. It's sure to be unforgettably delicious!
